{
  "policy": "measured-audible-bounds-v2",
  "voice": "zh-CN-YunxiaNeural",
  "rate": "+50%",
  "maximumInterUtteranceGap": 0.45,
  "chapters": [
    {
      "chapter": "前言",
      "duration": 34.2,
      "utterances": [
        {
          "id": "chapter-01-p01-u01",
          "text": "你的 AI 智能体为什么做着做着就忘了长期任务的目标？",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.158,
          "audioStart": 0,
          "spokenStart": 0.158,
          "spokenEnd": 3.372
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-01-p01-u02",
          "text": "因为信息还在，不等于重点还在。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.16,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.16,
          "audioStart": 3.388,
          "spokenStart": 3.532,
          "spokenEnd": 5.32
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-01-p02-u01",
          "text": "Anthropic 的上下文工程给出关键原因：上下文是一份有限的注意力预算。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.45,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.45,
          "audioStart": 5.616,
          "spokenStart": 5.77,
          "spokenEnd": 9.797
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-01-p02-u02",
          "text": "旧决策、工具输出和原始历史越多，下一步信号越弱。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.16,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.16,
          "audioStart": 9.817,
          "spokenStart": 9.957,
          "spokenEnd": 13.329
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-01-p03-u01",
          "text": "所以，喂得更多反而可能让 AI 智能体跑偏。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.22,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.22,
          "audioStart": 13.411,
          "spokenStart": 13.549,
          "spokenEnd": 16.31
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-01-p03-u02",
          "text": "接下来你会学会保住目标、按需检索，并持续更新工作状态。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.16,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.16,
          "audioStart": 16.328,
          "spokenStart": 16.47,
          "spokenEnd": 20.122
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-01-p04-u01",
          "text": "最后带走一份六部分高信号上下文包：目标、规则、工具、示例、检索和状态。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.22,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.22,
          "audioStart": 20.2,
          "spokenStart": 20.342,
          "spokenEnd": 25.449
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-01-p04-u02",
          "text": "先收藏，下一次长期任务直接套用。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.16,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.16,
          "audioStart": 25.461,
          "spokenStart": 25.609,
          "spokenEnd": 27.922
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-01-p05-u01",
          "text": "核心判断只有一句：给 AI 智能体支持下一步行动的最小充分上下文，并随着长期任务持续更新。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.22,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.22,
          "audioStart": 27.995,
          "spokenStart": 28.142,
          "spokenEnd": 33.95
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "chapter": "注意力预算",
      "duration": 78.333333,
      "utterances": [
        {
          "id": "chapter-02-p01-u01",
          "text": "上下文包含模型生成下一次回复时能看到的全部 token：系统指令、工具定义、示例、检索到的文档、消息历史、中间结果和当前请求。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.32,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.146,
          "audioStart": 0,
          "spokenStart": 0.146,
          "spokenEnd": 8.935
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-02-p01-u02",
          "text": "上下文工程管理的是这整个状态，不只是开头那一段提示词。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.16,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.16,
          "audioStart": 8.947,
          "spokenStart": 9.095,
          "spokenEnd": 12.474
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-02-p02-u01",
          "text": "Anthropic 把上下文描述为有限资源，而且新增内容的边际收益会下降。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.22,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.22,
          "audioStart": 12.542,
          "spokenStart": 12.694,
          "spokenEnd": 16.694
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-02-p02-u02",
          "text": "有关 context rot 的研究反复看到一种现象：材料越多，模型越可能难以准确找回藏在其中的相关信息。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.16,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.16,
          "audioStart": 16.702,
          "spokenStart": 16.854,
          "spokenEnd": 22.961
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-02-p02-u03",
          "text": "窗口更大，不代表注意力免费。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.16,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.16,
          "audioStart": 22.98,
          "spokenStart": 23.121,
          "spokenEnd": 24.801
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-02-p03-u01",
          "text": "这解释了为什么超长提示词仍会失败。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.22,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.22,
          "audioStart": 24.873,
          "spokenStart": 25.021,
          "spokenEnd": 27.352
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-02-p03-u02",
          "text": "正确规则可能确实写进去了，但周围还有过期计划、重复说明、原始日志和一长串边缘情况。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.16,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.16,
          "audioStart": 27.369,
          "spokenStart": 27.512,
          "spokenEnd": 33.484
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-02-p03-u03",
          "text": "智能体在解决任务前，先要猜哪些内容仍然有效、权威而且与当前步骤有关。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.16,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.16,
          "audioStart": 33.493,
          "spokenStart": 33.644,
          "spokenEnd": 38.332
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-02-p04-u01",
          "text": "所以，好的上下文工程首先是筛选。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.22,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.22,
          "audioStart": 38.41,
          "spokenStart": 38.552,
          "spokenEnd": 40.737
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-02-p04-u02",
          "text": "每个关键步骤开始前，都问一句：什么信息会改变下一步判断？",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.24,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.24,
          "audioStart": 40.826,
          "spokenStart": 40.977,
          "spokenEnd": 44.644
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-02-p04-u03",
          "text": "保留目标、必要约束、当前证据和实时状态；能够稍后获取的参考细节，只保留索引。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.16,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.16,
          "audioStart": 44.649,
          "spokenStart": 44.804,
          "spokenEnd": 50.178
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-02-p05-u01",
          "text": "筛选还要持续进行。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.22,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.22,
          "audioStart": 50.249,
          "spokenStart": 50.398,
          "spokenEnd": 51.547
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-02-p05-u02",
          "text": "工具调用带来新证据，错误暴露新边界，完成里程碑后，原始轨迹可以换成紧凑状态摘要。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.16,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.16,
          "audioStart": 51.55,
          "spokenStart": 51.707,
          "spokenEnd": 57.173
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-02-p05-u03",
          "text": "第十步需要的上下文，不会和第一步完全一样。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.16,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.16,
          "audioStart": 57.183,
          "spokenStart": 57.333,
          "spokenEnd": 59.904
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-02-p06-u01",
          "text": "最小不等于短。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.22,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.22,
          "audioStart": 59.982,
          "spokenStart": 60.124,
          "spokenEnd": 60.906
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-02-p06-u02",
          "text": "复杂迁移仍可能需要完整验收条件、仓库约定和风险控制。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.16,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.16,
          "audioStart": 60.926,
          "spokenStart": 61.066,
          "spokenEnd": 64.787
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-02-p06-u03",
          "text": "标准不是字最少，而是足以支持预期行为的最小集合。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.16,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.16,
          "audioStart": 64.799,
          "spokenStart": 64.947,
          "spokenEnd": 67.924
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-02-p07-u01",
          "text": "小结。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.22,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.22,
          "audioStart": 67.996,
          "spokenStart": 68.144,
          "spokenEnd": 68.555
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-02-p07-u02",
          "text": "第一，把上下文当作有限注意力预算，而不是无限存储。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.16,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.16,
          "audioStart": 68.567,
          "spokenStart": 68.715,
          "spokenEnd": 71.935
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-02-p08-u01",
          "text": "第二，更多 token 可能稀释下一步最重要的指令。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.22,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.22,
          "audioStart": 72,
          "spokenStart": 72.155,
          "spokenEnd": 74.704
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-02-p09-u01",
          "text": "第三，保留最小充分集合，并随任务变化持续刷新。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.22,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.22,
          "audioStart": 74.774,
          "spokenStart": 74.924,
          "spokenEnd": 78.068
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "chapter": "高信号输入",
      "duration": 73.366667,
      "utterances": [
        {
          "id": "chapter-03-p01-u01",
          "text": "先把系统指令写在合适的抽象层级。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.32,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.15,
          "audioStart": 0,
          "spokenStart": 0.15,
          "spokenEnd": 2.303
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-03-p01-u02",
          "text": "一端是把所有分支硬编码成脆弱的规则；另一端只是说“把事情做好”，默认智能体知道没有明说的标准。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.16,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.16,
          "audioStart": 2.308,
          "spokenStart": 2.463,
          "spokenEnd": 8.573
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-03-p02-u01",
          "text": "更有效的中间位置会明确目标、边界和判断原则，同时给推理留下空间。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.22,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.22,
          "audioStart": 8.644,
          "spokenStart": 8.793,
          "spokenEnd": 13.271
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-03-p02-u02",
          "text": "背景、指令、工具说明和输出要求可以分区组织。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.16,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.16,
          "audioStart": 13.287,
          "spokenStart": 13.431,
          "spokenEnd": 16.638
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-03-p02-u03",
          "text": "格式有帮助，但真正决定效果的是内容是否清楚、优先级是否明确。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.16,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.16,
          "audioStart": 16.649,
          "spokenStart": 16.798,
          "spokenEnd": 21.023
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-03-p03-u01",
          "text": "接着检查工具。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.22,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.22,
          "audioStart": 21.102,
          "spokenStart": 21.243,
          "spokenEnd": 22.016
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-03-p03-u02",
          "text": "工具不只是一个动作，还是智能体与环境之间的契约。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.16,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.16,
          "audioStart": 22.025,
          "spokenStart": 22.176,
          "spokenEnd": 25.052
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-03-p03-u03",
          "text": "名称、说明、参数、错误处理和返回数据都会进入上下文，并影响智能体选择哪一个动作。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.16,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.16,
          "audioStart": 25.06,
          "spokenStart": 25.212,
          "spokenEnd": 30.944
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-03-p04-u01",
          "text": "功能重叠会制造模糊决策，也会浪费注意力。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.22,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.22,
          "audioStart": 31.011,
          "spokenStart": 31.164,
          "spokenEnd": 33.784
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-03-p04-u02",
          "text": "如果人都说不清两个工具分别什么时候使用，就不能期待智能体稳定判断。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.16,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.16,
          "audioStart": 33.795,
          "spokenStart": 33.944,
          "spokenEnd": 38.161
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-03-p04-u03",
          "text": "保留最小可用工具集，让每个工具职责单一、输入明确、结果紧凑。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.16,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.16,
          "audioStart": 38.166,
          "spokenStart": 38.321,
          "spokenEnd": 42.316
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-03-p05-u01",
          "text": "然后筛选示例。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.22,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.22,
          "audioStart": 42.394,
          "spokenStart": 42.536,
          "spokenEnd": 43.344
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-03-p05-u02",
          "text": "堆满边缘情况看起来很全面，却容易把规律埋掉。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.16,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.16,
          "audioStart": 43.357,
          "spokenStart": 43.504,
          "spokenEnd": 46.459
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-03-p05-u03",
          "text": "Anthropic 更推荐少量、多样、典型的例子，让智能体看见预期模式、必要变化和一条重要边界。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.16,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.16,
          "audioStart": 46.467,
          "spokenStart": 46.619,
          "spokenEnd": 52.293
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-03-p06-u01",
          "text": "高信号不是固定字数。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.22,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.22,
          "audioStart": 52.363,
          "spokenStart": 52.513,
          "spokenEnd": 53.809
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-03-p06-u02",
          "text": "它指一段信息有明确工作：确定结果、约束行为、选择工具、展示模式、提供证据或暴露停止条件。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.16,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.16,
          "audioStart": 53.822,
          "spokenStart": 53.969,
          "spokenEnd": 60.238
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-03-p06-u03",
          "text": "只有完全不承担这些工作时，才应该删除。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.16,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.16,
          "audioStart": 60.242,
          "spokenStart": 60.398,
          "spokenEnd": 62.783
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-03-p07-u01",
          "text": "小结。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.22,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.22,
          "audioStart": 62.855,
          "spokenStart": 63.003,
          "spokenEnd": 63.414
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-03-p07-u02",
          "text": "第一，系统指令要落在硬编码和空泛之间的合适层级。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.16,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.16,
          "audioStart": 63.429,
          "spokenStart": 63.574,
          "spokenEnd": 66.721
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-03-p08-u01",
          "text": "第二，工具要清楚、高效，并尽量减少功能重叠。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.22,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.22,
          "audioStart": 66.796,
          "spokenStart": 66.941,
          "spokenEnd": 69.971
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-03-p09-u01",
          "text": "第三，用少量典型示例教会智能体真正的模式。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.22,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.22,
          "audioStart": 70.042,
          "spokenStart": 70.191,
          "spokenEnd": 73.119
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "chapter": "按需检索",
      "duration": 75.033333,
      "utterances": [
        {
          "id": "chapter-04-p01-u01",
          "text": "不少系统会在智能体开始前，把所有可能相关的文档全部塞进上下文。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.32,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.15,
          "audioStart": 0,
          "spokenStart": 0.15,
          "spokenEnd": 4.235
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-04-p01-u02",
          "text": "材料少而稳定时，这样做很快；但智能体还不知道哪一段真正重要，注意力预算已经提前花掉了。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.16,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.16,
          "audioStart": 4.258,
          "spokenStart": 4.395,
          "spokenEnd": 10.075
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-04-p02-u01",
          "text": "按需检索只保留轻量引用，比如文件路径、已保存查询、网页链接、对象标识、目录名和时间戳。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.22,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.22,
          "audioStart": 10.147,
          "spokenStart": 10.295,
          "spokenEnd": 16.563
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-04-p02-u02",
          "text": "上下文里保留地图，到了某个判断确实需要证据时，再打开对应内容。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.16,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.16,
          "audioStart": 16.579,
          "spokenStart": 16.723,
          "spokenEnd": 20.753
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-04-p03-u01",
          "text": "这会形成渐进式披露。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.22,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.22,
          "audioStart": 20.827,
          "spokenStart": 20.973,
          "spokenEnd": 22.166
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-04-p03-u02",
          "text": "文件名提示用途，目录结构说明关系，文件大小暗示复杂度，一次搜索结果帮助缩小下一次查询。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.16,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.16,
          "audioStart": 22.173,
          "spokenStart": 22.326,
          "spokenEnd": 28.239
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-04-p03-u03",
          "text": "智能体逐层建立理解，同时只把正在使用的子集放进工作上下文。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.16,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.16,
          "audioStart": 28.25,
          "spokenStart": 28.399,
          "spokenEnd": 32.292
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-04-p04-u01",
          "text": "Claude Code 就体现了这种方法。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.22,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.22,
          "audioStart": 32.363,
          "spokenStart": 32.512,
          "spokenEnd": 34.052
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-04-p04-u02",
          "text": "稳定的项目指令可以预先加载，文件搜索、grep、head 和 tail 负责查看大仓库里的目标片段，不必一次读取所有文件正文。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.16,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.16,
          "audioStart": 34.059,
          "spokenStart": 34.212,
          "spokenEnd": 41.427
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-04-p05-u01",
          "text": "取舍同样真实。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.22,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.22,
          "audioStart": 41.502,
          "spokenStart": 41.647,
          "spokenEnd": 42.569
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-04-p05-u02",
          "text": "运行时探索比预加载更慢，导航不佳还会让智能体在错误方向上浪费 token。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.16,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.16,
          "audioStart": 42.573,
          "spokenStart": 42.729,
          "spokenEnd": 47.417
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-04-p05-u03",
          "text": "它需要合适的搜索工具、能说明用途的命名，以及知道什么时候停止探索的规则。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.16,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.16,
          "audioStart": 47.427,
          "spokenStart": 47.577,
          "spokenEnd": 52.115
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-04-p06-u01",
          "text": "因此更实用的是混合策略。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.22,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.22,
          "audioStart": 52.19,
          "spokenStart": 52.335,
          "spokenEnd": 53.786
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-04-p06-u02",
          "text": "预先放入稳定规则、当前目标和几乎每一步都会用到的少量事实；变化快、细节多或很少使用的材料放到检索入口后面。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.16,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.16,
          "audioStart": 53.798,
          "spokenStart": 53.946,
          "spokenEnd": 61.594
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-04-p06-u03",
          "text": "边界要根据任务和漏掉信息的代价来定。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.16,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.16,
          "audioStart": 61.605,
          "spokenStart": 61.754,
          "spokenEnd": 64.021
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-04-p07-u01",
          "text": "小结。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.22,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.22,
          "audioStart": 64.093,
          "spokenStart": 64.241,
          "spokenEnd": 64.652
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-04-p07-u02",
          "text": "第一，保留轻量引用，不要预先塞入全部正文。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.16,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.16,
          "audioStart": 64.666,
          "spokenStart": 64.812,
          "spokenEnd": 67.566
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-04-p08-u01",
          "text": "第二，让 AI 智能体在细节真正相关时再逐步发现。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.22,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.22,
          "audioStart": 67.633,
          "spokenStart": 67.786,
          "spokenEnd": 71.158
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-04-p09-u01",
          "text": "第三，在更聚焦的上下文和额外检索成本之间做取舍。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.22,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.22,
          "audioStart": 71.231,
          "spokenStart": 71.378,
          "spokenEnd": 74.761
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "chapter": "长任务记忆",
      "duration": 73.566667,
      "utterances": [
        {
          "id": "chapter-05-p01-u01",
          "text": "长任务还会带来第二个问题。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.32,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.146,
          "audioStart": 0,
          "spokenStart": 0.146,
          "spokenEnd": 1.72
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-05-p01-u02",
          "text": "即使上下文一直被认真筛选，智能体执行动作、观察结果、修复错误和累积决定后，窗口仍会填满。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.16,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.16,
          "audioStart": 1.739,
          "spokenStart": 1.88,
          "spokenEnd": 8.098
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-05-p01-u03",
          "text": "连续工作几小时，可能多次超过可用范围。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.16,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.16,
          "audioStart": 8.106,
          "spokenStart": 8.258,
          "spokenEnd": 10.657
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-05-p02-u01",
          "text": "第一种方法是压缩。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.22,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.22,
          "audioStart": 10.729,
          "spokenStart": 10.877,
          "spokenEnd": 11.908
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-05-p02-u02",
          "text": "把对话或轨迹总结后开启新窗口，只带上保持连续性所需的决定、未解决问题、约束、证据和下一步动作。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.16,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.16,
          "audioStart": 11.913,
          "spokenStart": 12.068,
          "spokenEnd": 18.706
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-05-p02-u03",
          "text": "已经完成使命的原始工具输出通常可以退出。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.16,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.16,
          "audioStart": 18.713,
          "spokenStart": 18.866,
          "spokenEnd": 21.33
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-05-p03-u01",
          "text": "压缩存在风险：今天看起来次要的细节，可能后来才显出关键价值。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.22,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.22,
          "audioStart": 21.399,
          "spokenStart": 21.55,
          "spokenEnd": 25.785
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-05-p03-u02",
          "text": "Anthropic 建议先追求高召回，再逐步提高精确度。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.16,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.16,
          "audioStart": 25.79,
          "spokenStart": 25.945,
          "spokenEnd": 28.718
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-05-p03-u03",
          "text": "多带一点内容，通常比丢掉决定性约束更安全。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.16,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.16,
          "audioStart": 28.724,
          "spokenStart": 28.878,
          "spokenEnd": 31.446
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-05-p04-u01",
          "text": "第二种方法是结构化笔记。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.22,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.22,
          "audioStart": 31.518,
          "spokenStart": 31.666,
          "spokenEnd": 33.23
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-05-p04-u02",
          "text": "智能体把进度、里程碑、发现和开放问题写到窗口之外，需要时再取回相关部分。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.16,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.16,
          "audioStart": 33.239,
          "spokenStart": 33.39,
          "spokenEnd": 38.46
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-05-p04-u03",
          "text": "这样能保留持久工作状态，又不用让整段对话一直在线。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.16,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.16,
          "audioStart": 38.47,
          "spokenStart": 38.62,
          "spokenEnd": 41.958
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-05-p05-u01",
          "text": "专门的 Agent 可以隔离深度探索。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.22,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.22,
          "audioStart": 42.023,
          "spokenStart": 42.178,
          "spokenEnd": 43.878
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-05-p05-u02",
          "text": "主 Agent 保留高层计划，多个专门 Agent 分别研究独立问题，再把压缩后的发现交回。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.16,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.16,
          "audioStart": 43.888,
          "spokenStart": 44.038,
          "spokenEnd": 48.93
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-05-p05-u03",
          "text": "只有并行深挖的价值超过协调成本时，这种方式才值得。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.16,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.16,
          "audioStart": 48.935,
          "spokenStart": 49.09,
          "spokenEnd": 52.394
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-05-p06-u01",
          "text": "选择要看任务形态：持续对话用压缩，有清晰里程碑的迭代工作用笔记，独立而复杂的研究用专门 Agent。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.22,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.22,
          "audioStart": 52.471,
          "spokenStart": 52.614,
          "spokenEnd": 58.717
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-05-p06-u02",
          "text": "无论采用哪种方式，交接都必须保留目标、决定、证据、未知项和下一步动作。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.16,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.16,
          "audioStart": 58.729,
          "spokenStart": 58.877,
          "spokenEnd": 63.706
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-05-p07-u01",
          "text": "小结。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.22,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.22,
          "audioStart": 63.778,
          "spokenStart": 63.926,
          "spokenEnd": 64.337
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-05-p07-u02",
          "text": "第一，把长轨迹压缩成高召回的连续性摘要。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.16,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.16,
          "audioStart": 64.349,
          "spokenStart": 64.497,
          "spokenEnd": 66.971
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-05-p08-u01",
          "text": "第二，把持久工作状态写进结构化外部笔记。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.22,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.22,
          "audioStart": 67.044,
          "spokenStart": 67.191,
          "spokenEnd": 69.832
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-05-p09-u01",
          "text": "第三，只有聚焦探索值得协调成本时，才使用专门 Agent。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.22,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.22,
          "audioStart": 69.901,
          "spokenStart": 70.052,
          "spokenEnd": 73.306
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "chapter": "上下文包",
      "duration": 71.666667,
      "utterances": [
        {
          "id": "chapter-06-p01-u01",
          "text": "把前面的方法整理成一份最小高信号上下文包。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.32,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.15,
          "audioStart": 0,
          "spokenStart": 0.15,
          "spokenEnd": 2.906
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-06-p01-u02",
          "text": "它有六部分：结果目标、运行规则、工具地图、典型示例、检索索引和工作状态。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.16,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.16,
          "audioStart": 2.917,
          "spokenStart": 3.066,
          "spokenEnd": 8.271
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-06-p01-u03",
          "text": "它足够紧凑，可以人工检查；也足够完整，可以支持真实工作。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.16,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.16,
          "audioStart": 8.283,
          "spokenStart": 8.431,
          "spokenEnd": 12.256
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-06-p02-u01",
          "text": "第一部分是结果目标。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.22,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.22,
          "audioStart": 12.332,
          "spokenStart": 12.476,
          "spokenEnd": 13.583
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-06-p02-u02",
          "text": "写清目标、使用者、交付物、验收条件，以及结果要支持的决定。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.16,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.16,
          "audioStart": 13.603,
          "spokenStart": 13.743,
          "spokenEnd": 17.727
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-06-p02-u03",
          "text": "这样可以避免智能体做出很流畅、很好看，却没有解决真实问题的产物。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.16,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.16,
          "audioStart": 17.743,
          "spokenStart": 17.887,
          "spokenEnd": 22.171
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-06-p03-u01",
          "text": "第二部分是运行规则。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.22,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.22,
          "audioStart": 22.245,
          "spokenStart": 22.391,
          "spokenEnd": 23.581
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-06-p03-u02",
          "text": "记录硬约束、权限、风险边界、升级节点和停止条件。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.16,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.16,
          "audioStart": 23.6,
          "spokenStart": 23.741,
          "spokenEnd": 27.326
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-06-p03-u03",
          "text": "把长期规则与临时假设分开，避免一次性的绕行方案悄悄变成永久政策。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.16,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.16,
          "audioStart": 27.33,
          "spokenStart": 27.486,
          "spokenEnd": 31.91
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-06-p04-u01",
          "text": "第三部分是工具地图和典型示例。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.22,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.22,
          "audioStart": 31.989,
          "spokenStart": 32.13,
          "spokenEnd": 34.297
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-06-p04-u02",
          "text": "每个工具写明使用条件、输入、紧凑输出，以及它不能替代的相邻工具；再加入两三个例子，展示主要模式和一条关键边界。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.16,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.16,
          "audioStart": 34.305,
          "spokenStart": 34.457,
          "spokenEnd": 42.027
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-06-p05-u01",
          "text": "第四部分是检索索引。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.22,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.22,
          "audioStart": 42.098,
          "spokenStart": 42.247,
          "spokenEnd": 43.653
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-06-p05-u02",
          "text": "给每份来源保存轻量入口、用途标签和打开条件。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.16,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.16,
          "audioStart": 43.663,
          "spokenStart": 43.813,
          "spokenEnd": 47.075
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-06-p05-u03",
          "text": "智能体不仅要知道证据在哪里，也要知道什么时候必须取回证据。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.16,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.16,
          "audioStart": 47.081,
          "spokenStart": 47.235,
          "spokenEnd": 50.849
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-06-p06-u01",
          "text": "第五部分是工作状态。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.22,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.22,
          "audioStart": 50.922,
          "spokenStart": 51.069,
          "spokenEnd": 52.197
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-06-p06-u02",
          "text": "记录已完成事项、当前重点、关键决定与证据、未决问题、失败方法和下一步动作。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.16,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.16,
          "audioStart": 52.216,
          "spokenStart": 52.357,
          "spokenEnd": 57.561
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-06-p06-u03",
          "text": "到达里程碑就更新状态，再压缩或归档它替代的原始轨迹。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.16,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.16,
          "audioStart": 57.567,
          "spokenStart": 57.721,
          "spokenEnd": 61.041
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-06-p07-u01",
          "text": "小结。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.22,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.22,
          "audioStart": 61.113,
          "spokenStart": 61.261,
          "spokenEnd": 61.672
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-06-p07-u02",
          "text": "第一，用结果目标和运行规则锚定 AI 智能体。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.16,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.16,
          "audioStart": 61.683,
          "spokenStart": 61.832,
          "spokenEnd": 64.632
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-06-p08-u01",
          "text": "第二，用工具地图、典型示例和检索索引指导行动。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.22,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.22,
          "audioStart": 64.704,
          "spokenStart": 64.852,
          "spokenEnd": 68.178
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-06-p09-u01",
          "text": "第三，用紧凑且持续更新的工作状态保持连续性。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.22,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.22,
          "audioStart": 68.25,
          "spokenStart": 68.398,
          "spokenEnd": 71.402
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "chapter": "总结",
      "duration": 37.033333,
      "utterances": [
        {
          "id": "chapter-07-p01-u01",
          "text": "AI 智能体忘记重点，不只因为缺信息，也可能因为没有区分的信息太多，共同争夺有限注意力。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.32,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.154,
          "audioStart": 0,
          "spokenStart": 0.154,
          "spokenEnd": 5.65
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-07-p02-u01",
          "text": "第一，管理完整上下文状态，不只优化提示词。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.22,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.22,
          "audioStart": 5.722,
          "spokenStart": 5.87,
          "spokenEnd": 8.752
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-07-p02-u02",
          "text": "根据下一步判断需要什么，保留目标、约束、工具、证据和当前状态。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.16,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.16,
          "audioStart": 8.763,
          "spokenStart": 8.912,
          "spokenEnd": 13.353
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-07-p03-u01",
          "text": "第二，提高信号质量。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.22,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.22,
          "audioStart": 13.425,
          "spokenStart": 13.573,
          "spokenEnd": 14.75
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-07-p03-u02",
          "text": "用合适层级的指令、最小工具集和少量典型示例，替代脆弱规则与边缘情况堆积。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.16,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.16,
          "audioStart": 14.761,
          "spokenStart": 14.91,
          "spokenEnd": 20.12
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-07-p04-u01",
          "text": "第三，按需检索细节。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.22,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.22,
          "audioStart": 20.192,
          "spokenStart": 20.34,
          "spokenEnd": 21.717
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-07-p04-u02",
          "text": "稳定且高频的信息放在前面，变化快或专业性强的材料通过明确引用逐步打开。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.16,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.16,
          "audioStart": 21.722,
          "spokenStart": 21.877,
          "spokenEnd": 26.911
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-07-p05-u01",
          "text": "最后，用压缩、结构化笔记和六部分最小高信号上下文包保护长任务。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.22,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.22,
          "audioStart": 26.986,
          "spokenStart": 27.131,
          "spokenEnd": 31.421
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-07-p05-u02",
          "text": "保留信号，按需取细节，持续维护工作状态。",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.16,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.16,
          "audioStart": 31.433,
          "spokenStart": 31.581,
          "spokenEnd": 34.309
        },
        {
          "id": "chapter-07-p06-u01",
          "text": "关注 Tiny Agent，成为更擅长使用 AI 的人！",
          "desiredGapBefore": 0.22,
          "actualGapBefore": 0.22,
          "audioStart": 34.376,
          "spokenStart": 34.529,
          "spokenEnd": 36.78
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
